  <section style="border-top: 1px solid darkgray; padding-top: 6em; padding-bottom: 6em;" class="bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <div class="d-sm-flex justify-content-center">
            <div class="pr-4">
              <h3 class="h2-styles">What is cryptcurrency?</h3>
              <p class="lead">
                  Cryptocurrencies are digital currencies. The 'crypto' bit refers to the 
                  mechanisms used to validate them. Bitcoin is the most well
                  known, although there are many others. CoinFunnel supports the 
                  Monero currency, because this can be mined easily on most home computers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  
  <section style="border-top: 1px solid darkgray; padding-top: 6em; padding-bottom: 6em;" class="px-2 bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <h3 class="h2-styles">What is mining?</h3>
          <p class="lead">
            'Mining' cryptocurrency is the process of creating digital currency 
            using a computer. It is not normally important to understand the 
            mining process in detail, any more than it is important to understand 
            network protocols just to use the Internet. However, here is a 
            simplified overview:
          </p>

          <p class="lead">
            Specialist mining software performs 'guesses', known technically as 'hashes',
            where it will generate a random number, then compare this number
            against the number that is created when all recent crypto transactions
            (a block) are summarised by a single number. If that numbers match, then 
            the 'guess' was successful and the software has successfully 'mined a block',
            for which you will receive a crypto reward. CoinFunnel ensures that the
            reward to sent to the charity you are mining for.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="border-top: 1px solid darkgray; padding-top: 6em; padding-bottom: 6em;" class="bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <h3 class="h2-styles">Charities</h3>
          <div class="row">

            <div class="col-sm text-center p-4 lead mt-1 mx-1" style="border: 1px solid darkgray;">
                <h4>Step 1</h4>
                Register for free and add your charity details to be listed on this site
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm text-center p-4 lead mt-1 mx-1" style="border: 1px solid darkgray;">
                <h4>Step 2</h4>
                Download and try out your personalised mining application, to see how it works
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm text-center p-4 lead mt-1 mx-1" style="border: 1px solid darkgray;">
                <h4>Step 3</h4>
                Spread the word to your supporters using the social media links
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="border-top: 1px solid darkgray; padding-top: 6em; padding-bottom: 6em;" class="bg-secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <h3 class="h2-styles">Supporters</h3>
          <div class="row">

            <div class="col-sm text-center p-4 lead mt-1 mx-1" style="border: 1px solid darkgray;">
                <h4>Step 1</h4>
                Visit the <a href="/explore">Explore</a> page to browse
                the charities listed on this site
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm text-center p-4 lead mt-1 mx-1" style="border: 1px solid darkgray;">
                <h4>Step 2</h4>
